channel.title: HybridScape PvP V3 HELP!
channel.description: I just downloaded a fresh copy of the Hybridscape PvP V3 client and as soon as compile it I get like 100 errors, and when I try running the client it opens up the cmd for 1 sec then goes away. Nothing happens. I made sure I change the run.bat to match my jdk. It seems not many people have this problem, but i like the client, so id like to fix it. PLEASE HELP!!! :mad:

item.title: HybridScape PvP V3 HELP!
item.dc:creator: @gergy008 gergy008
item.description:
@gergy008 wrote:

in the .bat place this after the last line:

PAUSE

That will pause the errors and let you see whats going on. Alt+Print screen (Much easier) the errors onto here so we can look.
